column1: Looking for someone to help you learn a language or give you expert advice?  Looking for an interface where you can provide services without paying for gas or an overpriced cup of coffee?  At Aimya, you can advertise your services or what services you need.  You can also browse our database of Student and Teaching users for what you’re looking for.  All you need to do to get started is create a student profile for free.
column2: 你是不是正在寻找一个能够帮助你学习语言或者提供专家建议的老师？你是不是正在寻找一个不需要花费油钱和高价格的咖啡的平台？在Aimya，你可以提供你的服务或者得到你想要的服务。你可以浏览想要寻找的学生和老师的资料库。你所需要做的仅仅是免费创建一个账号。
